<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-11.Businessrules">11. Business r=
ules</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Canonical kind is set only for cross-language abstractions; language-spe=
cific symbols may have no canonical kind.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>language_kind</code> preserves parser-native node kind.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Resolution order is deterministic: local -&gt; import alias -&gt; unreso=
lved fallback.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Default DevQL artefact and dependency queries operate on current-state t=
ables unless a historical selector is provided.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>asOf(commit/ref)</code> uses historical committed tables.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>asOf(saveRevision:...)</code> uses current-state tables filtered t=
o the specified temporary revision.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>symbol_id</code> remains stable across non-semantic line moves and=
 formatting-only edits.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>artefact_id</code> is revision/blob-specific and may change when b=
lob content changes.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>devql ingest</code> promotes temporary current rows only when the =
blob in temporary state matches the blob at <code>HEAD</code> for that path=
.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>implements</code> is emitted from implementation constructs such a=
s Rust <code>impl Trait for Type</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>extends</code> is the canonical relation for class/interface exten=
sion and Rust supertrait relationships.</p></li>
<li>
<p>If a macro edge is emitted, it uses <code>call_form=3D"macro"</code>; un=
resolved macro fallback is not required in V1.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Re-ingest on changed code updates emitted data and preserves logical ded=
up.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.DevQLcapabilitiesandexamples"=
>12. DevQL capabilities and examples</h2>
<p>This feature enables more than a static ingest. DevQL can answer questio=
ns about the <strong>current workspace</strong>, a <strong>temporary local =
revision</strong>, or a <strong>historical committed snapshot</strong>.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.1Listcurrentsymbolsinafile">1=
2.1 List current symbols in a file</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;file("src/main.ts")-&gt;artefacts(k=
ind:"function")-&gt;limit(10)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>Use this to inspect the functions currently indexed for a file in the li=
ve workspace state.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.2Currentblastradiusforasymbol=
">12.2 Current blast radius for a symbol</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("temp2")-&gt;artefacts(symbol_fqn:"src/target.ts::targe=
t")-&gt;deps(kind:"calls",direction:"in")-&gt;limit(10)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This returns callers of <code>src/target.ts::target</code> from the curr=
ent graph.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.3Currentoutgoingdependenciesf=
orafunction">12.3 Current outgoing dependencies for a function</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;file("src/main.ts")-&gt;artefacts(k=
ind:"function")-&gt;deps(kind:"calls",direction:"out",include_unresolved:fa=
lse)-&gt;limit(25)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>Use this to see what a function currently calls, excluding unresolved ed=
ges.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.4Historicalblastradiusatacomm=
it">12.4 Historical blast radius at a commit</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;asOf(commit:"abc123")-&gt;file("src=
/main.ts")-&gt;artefacts(kind:"function")-&gt;deps(kind:"calls",direction:"=
out")-&gt;limit(10)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This reads from historical committed rows, not the current workspace sta=
te.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.5Queryatemporarylocalrevision=
">12.5 Query a temporary local revision</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("temp2")-&gt;asOf(saveRevision:"temp:42")-&gt;artefacts=
(kind:"function")-&gt;deps(kind:"calls",direction:"both")-&gt;limit(10)'</p=
re>
</div>
</div>
<p>Use this when you want to inspect a specific temporary workspace revisio=
n instead of the latest current state.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.6Explicitlyquerycurrentsavedw=
orkspacestate">12.6 Explicitly query current saved workspace state</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;asOf(save:"current")-&gt;file("src/=
main.ts")-&gt;artefacts(kind:"function")-&gt;limit(10)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This is equivalent in routing to the default current-state query but mak=
es intent explicit.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.7Agent-awareartefactdiscovery=
">12.7 Agent-aware artefact discovery</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;artefacts(agent:"claude-code",since=
:"2026-03-01")-&gt;select(path,canonical_kind,symbol_fqn,start_line,end_lin=
e)-&gt;limit(50)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This filters artefacts by event-derived change history.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.8Chathistoryforindexedartefac=
ts">12.8 Chat history for indexed artefacts</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("bitloops-cli")-&gt;file("index.ts")-&gt;artefacts(line=
s:1..20,kind:"function")-&gt;chatHistory()-&gt;limit(5)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This enriches artefact results with relevant chat history context.</p>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-12.9Testscoveringaproductionarte=
fact">12.9 Tests covering a production artefact</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: bash; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">bitloop=
s devql query 'repo("r")-&gt;file("src/user/service.rs")-&gt;artefacts(kind=
:"function")-&gt;tests()-&gt;limit(10)'</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This returns linked test scenarios for the selected production artefacts=
.</p>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-13.Risksandlimitations">13. Risk=
s and limitations</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Live workspace indexing currently reflects structural artefacts and depe=
ndency edges first; semantic features, embeddings, and clone edges are upda=
ted during ingest.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The current watcher architecture should not be described as a generic, f=
ully reconciled, provider-agnostic indexing service.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Blast-radius answers can differ between current state and historical com=
mitted state by design; the page should call out which one is being queried=
.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Unresolved Rust macro calls may be intentionally dropped in V1 under the=
 current import/local resolution policy.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-14.Testplan">14. Test plan</h2>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-Unittests">Unit tests</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Canonical mapping (<code>language_kind -&gt; canonical_kind</code>)</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p><code>symbol_fqn</code> construction rules</p></li>
<li>
<p>TS/JS extraction for artefacts and edge kinds</p></li>
<li>
<p>Rust extraction for artefacts and edge kinds</p></li>
<li>
<p>Deterministic target resolution order</p></li>
<li>
<p>Symbol identity stability across line moves</p></li>
<li>
<p>Revision-specific artefact identity changes per blob</p></li>
<li>
<p>Parser normalization from legacy <code>inherits</code> to canonical <cod=
e>extends</code></p></li>
<li>
<p>Current-state schema constraints and indexes</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-Integrationtests">Integration te=
sts</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Ingest + query roundtrip for mixed TS/JS + Rust fixture repos</p></li>
<li>
<p>Watcher/current-state update flow for local changes</p></li>
<li>
<p>Promotion of temporary current rows during ingest</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>deps(direction:"in"|"out"|"both")</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>asOf(commit/ref)</code> routing to historical tables</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>asOf(saveRevision:...)</code> routing to filtered current tables</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>Unresolved filtering</p></li>
<li>
<p>Repeated ingest dedup behavior</p></li>
<li>
<p>Export/re-export dedup behavior</p></li>
<li>
<p>Query output returns canonical <code>extends</code></p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-E2Etests">E2E tests</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Blast-radius user journey from current workspace state</p></li>
<li>
<p>Blast-radius user journey from historical committed state</p></li>
<li>
<p>Local edit -&gt; current query -&gt; ingest -&gt; promoted committed que=
ry</p></li>
<li>
<p>Locate symbol -&gt; query incoming dependencies -&gt; verify impacted fi=
les/symbols set</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-15.Dependencies">15. Dependencie=
s</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Internal services</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>DevQL watcher/current-state update path</p></li>
<li>
<p>DevQL ingest pipeline</p></li>
<li>
<p>DevQL query parser/executor</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>External libraries</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>tree-sitter</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>tree-sitter-javascript</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>tree-sitter-typescript</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>tree-sitter-rust</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><code>notify</code></p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Infrastructure/runtime dependencies</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Git CLI for tree and blob resolution</p></li>
<li>
<p>Relational storage (<code>sqlite</code> and/or <code>postgres</code>, de=
pending on environment)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Feature flags</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Optional parser rollout flag if needed</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Rollout strategy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Enable AST extraction and current-state indexing in staged validation en=
vironments first</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-16.Observabilityandrolloutnotes"=
>16. Observability and rollout notes</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Log promotion counts for temporary current rows during <code>devql inges=
t</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Track current-state update success/failure for watcher-driven batches.</=
p></li>
<li>
<p>Track parse failures separately from query failures.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Keep documentation explicit about which capabilities are current-state o=
nly, historical only, or ingest-refreshed.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"ArtefactCompletionandBlastRadius-17.DefinitionofDone">17. Definit=
ion of Done</h2>
<p>Feature is Done when:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>All BDD scenarios pass</p></li>
<li>
<p>Acceptance criteria are met</p></li>
<li>
<p>Unit and integration tests pass</p></li>
<li>
<p>Current-state indexing and historical query routing are documented</p></=
li>
<li>
<p>DevQL capabilities examples are documented and validated against support=
ed syntax</p></li>
<li>
<p>Observability counters/logs are enabled</p></li>
<li>
<p>No unresolved open questions block release</p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
